hopobject.body: What do you like doing in your spare time? is it safe to take viagra and cialis together It found that last winter almost seven in 10 households went without heating at some point to keep their energy costs down, while more than a third of people said cutting back on energy usage was affecting their quality of life or health. Almost nine in 10 people now think about the cost before switching on their heating, research from uSwitch found.
